preparations.

24:02.808 --> 24:06.211 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
HARI SREENIVASAN: When you see
these stories
and hear about these stories
across the country,

24:06.245 --> 24:11.483 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
