25:13.645 --> 25:14.179 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
perspective.

25:14.213 --> 25:16.181 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
HARI SREENIVASAN: Yes.

25:16.215 --> 25:18.384 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
DR. SHARON STANCLIFF: But also
getting Narcan,
or naloxone, when you are
actually opioid-dependent

25:18.417 --> 25:22.521 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
